
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 06 of Thoracic MRT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Upper abdomen, ascites' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Perihepatic' checkbox is enabled
And 'Perisplenic' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ascites, not further defined' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Ascites, not further defined' checkbox
Then 'Perihepatic' checkbox is disabled
And 'Perisplenic' checkbox is disabled
